It's official. Men love computers.

229
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:36,155
That's according to
the latest survey carried out

230
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:41,070
by popular men's leisure magazine
Popular Men's Leisure Magazine.

231
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:45,831
PMLM asked 2,000 men
to rank various leisure activities

232
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:47,872
in order of preference.

233
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:49,912
And, somewhat surprisingly,

234
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,919
using a home computer
comes top of the list,

235
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:57,239
beating some rather more traditional
male pursuits.

236
00:14:57,280 --> 00:15:02,071
So clearly men have taken computers
to heart. But what about women?

237
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:06,433
Well, PMLM carried out
the same survey for them

